---
title: Lamb Kofta & Couscous Mezze Plate with Sumac Cherry Tomato Salad & Dukkah Flatbreads
description: Turn a weeknight meal into a fun feast with this mixed platter of lamb kofta, a punchy sumac-infused cherry tomato salad,
dukkah-crusted flatbreads and creamy herb yoghurt. Pickled onion adds the perfect finishing touch for a plate of tasty treats
where every bite is different to the one before!
